{"tid":390682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人話蔡若蓮個仔同佢阿媽政見不合架喎","createTime":"2017-09-07T08:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T21:13:40.000Z","uid":16970,"like":226,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a841dbb7d0abfa45773b1dc9fdae125dc7bd5ac9","tid":390682,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"蔡若蓮可恨，但佢死嗰個仔係我細佬朋友&hellip;個阿媽唔著，個仔係知而且有出聲話阿媽。大家憎蔡若蓮都唔好過份涼薄同亂評&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n你哋覺得個阿媽冇良知，但個仔係我哋呢一代人啊，係判斷到是非嘅青年人啊，大家真係覺得好爽好心涼？<br />\n　<br />\n我唔係忽然大愛或企道德高地。我從來都唔詛咒人，就算係我認為邪惡嘅人有親人出事，我最多冇感覺，唔故作悲痛亦唔涼薄拍掌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gaisi.grace/posts/1878007749183317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgaisi.grace%2Fposts%2F1878007749183317&d=tkmTD006pdmnVmn%2Fno3as0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ed03e874\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gaisi.grace/posts/1878007749183317</a><br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇呢?"},{"pid":"aa3b9d128f8090d393478b50e90e77ae60658ff2","tid":390682,"uid":19557,"like":593,"dislike":8,"score":585,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:56:39.000Z","msg":"大家係慶祝蔡若蓮得到報應死左個仔 而唔係慶祝蔡若蓮個仔死左"},{"pid":"6404d1c1a0c9b373ed2e4edc911f08c7e37474eb","tid":390682,"uid":18271,"like":8,"dislike":158,"score":-150,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:00:03.000Z","msg":"等睇連登史上最大型連環車禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0673b2d576fbe36721964d5baa85a1febe1d49","tid":390682,"uid":16970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:00:18.000Z","msg":"只能夠講句投錯胎, 死後都不得安寧."},{"pid":"eb8ba3e9af8e2b3c8606eb7cfe6987c087bdcebf","tid":390682,"uid":39365,"like":183,"dislike":2,"score":181,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家係慶祝蔡若蓮得到報應死左個仔 而唔係慶祝蔡若蓮個仔死左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係, 無人針對緊個仔囉, 個仔死因唔係網民攻擊佢, 而係被阿媽逼死既, 唔好搞錯呀