><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/172023_780564fbb981a1582543e34eea4bd83c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F172023_780564fbb981a1582543e34eea4bd83c.jpg&h=ceebbf77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/172024_acb2699c250cab74997100f9324cfaba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F172024_acb2699c250cab74997100f9324cfaba.jpg&h=eec7aef8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/172028_df50e8662601108ee2f353ea3ebf727a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F172028_df50e8662601108ee2f353ea3ebf727a.jpg&h=26df409f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/172044_f3ced136e4a8effddc58d43f64c290d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F172044_f3ced136e4a8effddc58d43f64c290d8.jpg&h=b1e2b773&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a48503ecb9d01e81b6f36ec8b320c7af37503b6","tid":390682,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"賣港既就要冚家剷<br />\n<br />\nnothing more nothing less"},{"pid":"431bd4e840265cff8b1997e99f805fe1b2e81c6c","tid":390682,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家係慶祝蔡若蓮得到報應死左個仔 而唔係慶祝蔡若蓮個仔死左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係, 無人針對緊個仔囉, 個仔死因唔係網民攻擊佢, 而係被阿媽逼死既, 唔好搞錯呀</blockquote><br />\n咁我見到果啲話&quot;副局長你個仔係自殺會落地獄&quot;果啲post應該係我有幻覺啦.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係耶撚ge講法wor<br />\n冤有頭債有主你個post應該改個<br />\n「耶撚話xxxx」"},{"pid":"ff4c22058a24cb849f9dc5fd06bd4e05a32d5dea","tid":390682,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:22:25.000Z","msg":"下係咪搞錯左?<br />\n個個係鬧緊個老母有報應<br />\n唔係鬧死者抵死喎"},{"pid":"720276a0eb352eb84f06f62399e93bf656325456","tid":390682,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家係慶祝蔡若蓮得到報應死左個仔 而唔係慶祝蔡若蓮個仔死左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人真係好撚mean<br />\n個仔死同佢老母政治取向係兩回事<br />\n大家可以屌佢老母政治上仆街<br />\n但個仔死 係另一回事<br />\n可唔可以唔好咁對人不對事<br />\n<br />\n因為平日既政見而幸災樂禍好仆街<br />\n<br />\n死者係好男仔黎 唔值得大家咁話佢<br />\n有著咁既老母 唔通又係佢既錯？</blockquote><br />\n屌你係咪未get到人地意思<br />\n人地係針對條8婆，唔係佢個仔呀"},{"pid":"27d53e51beb9bf26f41077431d1b1453143194aa","tid":390682,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:23:19.000Z","msg":"咁就應該大義滅親"},{"pid":"218559928f12fa2fc0f01c2a7e87242cd432b74e","tid":390682,"uid":65074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家係慶祝蔡若蓮得到報應死左個仔 而唔係慶祝蔡若蓮個仔死左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係, 無人針對緊個仔囉, 個仔死因唔係網民攻擊佢, 而係被阿媽逼死既, 唔好搞錯呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之後應該有五毛偷換概念講連登笑個仔死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉真係好撚多<br />\n上帝可唔可以創造一個冇五毛ge forum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cf56248a5ed72975ff5a4fea567e8477d28986","tid":390682,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>始終係呀媽  都係企呀媽果面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大把連登仔企係伯母個邊"},{"pid":"a950b9242097244a983effdd418621572eb05f49","tid":390682,"uid":16970,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家係慶祝蔡若蓮得到報應死左個仔 而唔係慶祝蔡若蓮個仔死左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係, 無人針對緊個仔囉, 個仔死因唔係網民攻擊佢, 而係被阿媽逼死既, 唔好搞錯呀</blockquote><br />\n咁我見到果啲話&quot;副局長你個仔係自殺會落地獄&quot;果啲post應該係我有幻覺啦.</blockquote><br />\n我諗係你唔明人地抽咩啦</blockquote><br />\n可能我真係唔明, 不如你講解下?</blockquote><br />\n咁不如你講下點解認為呢句野係攻擊個死者</blockquote><br />\n咁不如你睇下樓下啲cap圖睇下覺唔覺得係&quot;攻擊死者&quot;啦.<br />\n<br />\n有條友釘咗, 你同佢無仇無怨, 都話佢會落